A4.text: Eileen Davidson originated the role of Ashley Abbott on The Young and the Restless in March 1982, beating out more than 100 candidates.

A5.text: Davidson signed a three-year contract with The Bold and the Beautiful to play her The Young and the Restless character Ashley Abbott.
